# ADR 0005 — Locked baseline: 8 cloud + 3 self-hosted, March-2026 cutoff

**Date:** 2026-07-04
**Status:** Accepted (per user message 2026-07-04)
**Supersedes:** ADR 0003 §3 (which proposed Qwen3.8B AWQ as T2 workhorse — rejected by user)
**Author:** Forge (claude-code session, with corrections from user push-back on rounds 1–4)

---

## 1. Decision

Lock the baseline matrix to **8 cloud + 3 self-hosted models**, with a **March-2026 recency cutoff** for both lists. Everything else is "candidate for later" and not in the eval matrix until it gets its own ADR.

### 1.1 Cloud baselines (routed `forge-dev → omniroute-dev → OpenRouter`)

| # | OR id | Canonical HF repo | params_b | ctx | OR $/M prompt | OR $/M completion | HF last_modified | recency |
|---|---|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---|---|
| 1 | `inclusionai/ling-2.6-flash` | (proprietary) | 104.0 (7.4 active) | 262 144 | $0.01 | $0.03 | n/a | ✓ |
| 2 | `ibm-granite/granite-4.0-h-micro` | `ibm-granite/granite-4.0-h-micro` | 3.20 | 131 000 | $0.017 | $0.112 | 2025-11-03 | **PRE-MARCH_2026** |
| 3 | `liquid/lfm-2-24b-a2b` | `LiquidAI/LFM2-24B-A2B` | 23.84 (MoE) | 128 000 | $0.03 | $0.12 | 2026-03-30 | ✓ |
| 4 | `arcee-ai/trinity-mini` | `arcee-ai/Trinity-Mini` | 26.12 (MoE 3B-active) | 131 072 | $0.045 | $0.15 | 2026-05-28 | ✓ |
| 5 | `ibm-granite/granite-4.1-8b` | `ibm-granite/granite-4.1-8b` | 8.79 | 131 072 | $0.05 | $0.10 | 2026-05-04 | ✓ |
| 6 | `poolside/laguna-xs-2.1` | `poolside/Laguna-XS-2.1` | 33.44 (MoE 3B-active) | 262 144 | $0.06 | $0.12 | 2026-07-02 | ✓ |
